---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="SenTeGuard">
    <section class="section-spacing">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
            <h1>Regain Control of Your Data</h1>
            <p class="max-w-2xl">
                SenTeGuard helps mission driven teams deploy generative AI with confident safeguards,
                persistent visibility, and dependable compliance workflows.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <form
                    class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center"
                    action="mailto:david@senteguard.com"
                    method="post"
                    enctype="text/plain"
                >
                    <label class="flex-1 text-sm text-gray-300">
                        Join our email list
                        <input
                            type="email"
                            name="email"
                            required
                            placeholder="you@example.com"
                            class="mt-2 w-full rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-black px-3 py-2 text-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none"
                        />
                    </label>
                    <button class="btn sm:w-auto" type="submit">Join</button>
                </form>
                <div>
                    <a class="btn btn-lg" href="mailto:david@senteguard.com">Request a Demo</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] md:items-start">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h2>Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    We are on the precipice of a Cognitive Security Revolution. Network security defends the wires.
                    Cognitive security defends the thoughts flowing through them. We see a future where defense programs,
                    Fortune-500 labs, and fast moving startups can unleash generative AI without leaking classified data,
                    trade secrets, or sacrifice public trust, uniting national security rigor with commercial creativity
                    under one protective shield.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card space-y-3">
                <h3>Focus Areas</h3>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                    <li>Mission ready AI deployments</li>
                    <li>Security by design for enterprise teams</li>
                    <li>Continuous assurance and auditing</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr] lg:items-center">
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <h2>What is Sente?</h2>
                <p>
                    In Go a sente move compels a response. The player with sente dictates the flow of the game, while the
                    opponent is on the back foot, also known as gote. In other words, sente is not just moving first once.
                    It is keeping the first mover advantage throughout the encounter.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="/images/go-board.png" alt="Go board with black and white stones" class="w-full rounded-xl" />
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="founder" class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr]">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
                    <img
                        src="/images/founder.png"
                        alt="Portrait of David Weidman"
                        class="h-32 w-32 rounded-full border border-gray-800 object-cover"
                    />
                    <div class="space-y-2">
                        <h2>Founder</h2>
                        <p class="text-lg text-white">
                            <a href="https://davidjweidman.com">David Weidman</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-base text-white">Harvard Kennedy School</h3>
                        <p>Master in Public Policy</p>
                        <p>Artificial Intelligence</p>
                        <p>Regulatory Compliance</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-base text-white">U.S. Army</h3>
                        <p>Cyberwarfare Officer</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-base text-white">United States Military Academy</h3>
                        <p>Artificial Intelligence</p>
                        <p>Mathematics</p>
                        <p>Computer Science</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card space-y-4">
                <p>
                    David brings a decade of national security and cyber operations experience to the private sector. A
                    graduate of West Point and a former Army Officer specializing in cyberwarfare, he has led teams
                    defending against advanced threats in both domestic and overseas assignments. He is currently a Master
                    Candidate in Public Policy (International &amp; Global Affairs) at the Harvard Kennedy School.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2>Services</h2>
                <p>Build safer AI deployments with offerings designed for public sector and enterprise teams.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="card space-y-3">
                    <h3>SenTeGuard</h3>
                    <p>Core cognitive security platform for end to end protection across LLM workflows.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card space-y-3">
                    <h3>Moyo</h3>
                    <p>Agentic monitoring layer that keeps data and model behavior aligned with mission intent.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card space-y-3">
                    <h3>Consulting</h3>
                    <p>Strategic guidance for policy, risk management, and integration of AI security controls.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2>Capabilities</h2>
                <p>High level coverage areas that reduce exposure and maintain trust.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
                <div class="card space-y-3">
                    <h3>Content Safety Scans</h3>
                    <p>Identify sensitive data, harmful output, and prompt leakage before it reaches users.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card space-y-3">
                    <h3>Real Time Threat Detection</h3>
                    <p>Monitor model behavior continuously to flag attacks, anomalies, and misuse.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card space-y-3">
                    <h3>Compliance Scanner</h3>
                    <p>Map AI workflows to policy requirements and surface gaps quickly.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-center">
            <div>
                <h2>Connect With Us</h2>
                <p>Stay close to product updates and research highlights.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                <a class="btn btn-outline" href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/senteguard/" aria-label="SenTeGuard on LinkedIn">
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path
                            d="M4.98 3.5C4.98 4.88 3.86 6 2.49 6 1.12 6 0 4.88 0 3.5 0 2.12 1.12 1 2.49 1c1.37 0 2.49 1.12 2.49 2.5ZM0.5 8.5h3.99V23H0.5zM8.5 8.5h3.82v1.98h.05c.53-1 1.82-2.05 3.74-2.05 4 0 4.74 2.64 4.74 6.08V23h-3.99v-6.93c0-1.65-.03-3.78-2.31-3.78-2.31 0-2.66 1.8-2.66 3.66V23H8.5z"
                        />
                    </svg>
                </a>
                <a class="btn btn-outline" href="https://www.youtube.com/@SenteGuard" aria-label="SenTeGuard on YouTube">
                    <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path
                            d="M23.5 6.2a3.02 3.02 0 0 0-2.13-2.13C19.5 3.5 12 3.5 12 3.5s-7.5 0-9.37.57A3.02 3.02 0 0 0 .5 6.2C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.5 5.8a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.13 2.13C4.5 20.5 12 20.5 12 20.5s7.5 0 9.37-.57a3.02 3.02 0 0 0 2.13-2.13c.5-1.87.5-5.8.5-5.8s0-3.93-.5-5.8ZM9.75 15.5v-7l6.1 3.5-6.1 3.5Z"
                        />
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-spacing border-t border-gray-900">
        <div class="grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1.1fr]">
            <div class="space-y-3">
                <h2>Hiring in Engineering and Sales</h2>
                <p>Introduce yourself and share how you can help build secure AI systems.</p>
            </div>
            <form
                class="card space-y-4"
                action="mailto:david@senteguard.com"
                method="post"
                enctype="text/plain"
            >
                <label class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                    Name
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        name="name"
                        required
                        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-black px-3 py-2 text-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none"
                    />
                </label>
                <label class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                    Email
                    <input
                        type="email"
                        name="email"
                        required
                        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-black px-3 py-2 text-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none"
                    />
                </label>
                <label class="flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
                    Message
                    <textarea
                        name="message"
                        rows="4"
                        required
                        class="rounded-lg border border-gray-800 bg-black px-3 py-2 text-white focus:border-primary focus:outline-none"
                    ></textarea>
                </label>
                <button class="btn" type="submit">Send</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
